title: Studio + 1 unfinished room
posting_body: -	Slate floors in kitchen and bathroom.
-	Bright (3 south facing windows + recessed lighting).
Its about 500 sq ft total, a studio + an unfinished room.
The studio is about 400 sq feet including kitchen, full bath and main area.
There is an unfinished room, ~100sq ft, which could function as a gear room (there are some benches), a dark room, an art space, or a large walk in closet.
$1425/month for rent and all bills (electricity, water, sewer, garbage, heat, high speed internet).
Easy parking in front of house.
